    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has browned, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
